OL,7,FA mum has admitted to using a company
OL,8,Fcredit card to spend more than
OL,9,F#180,000 on hundreds of ink
OL,10,Fcartridges, before selling them for
OL,11,F#200 each on eBay.
OL,13,FClaire Timmins, 34, worked as an
OL,14,Fadministration officer for Salford-
OL,15,Fbased recruitment consultancy company
OL,16,FMorson Group.
