OL,7,FAs part of her role, she had access to
OL,8,Fthe company's credit card, but in
OL,9,FFebruary 2024, the firm's managing
OL,10,Fdirector was handed an overview of the
OL,11,Foverhead costs which revealed an
OL,12,F'abnormally large' amount spent on
OL,13,Fprint cartridges.
OL,15,FMorson Group only required around four
OL,16,Fcartridges per month, yet the figures
OL,17,Fshowed many, many more had been bought.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
