OL,7,FAn internal investigation revealed
OL,8,Fthat Timmins had been making
OL,9,Funauthorised purchases, then either
OL,10,Fhiding the deliveries in meeting
OL,11,Frooms, or having them delivered to her
OL,12,Fhome address.
OL,14,FShe was then advertising them for sale
OL,15,Fon eBay, using a different name, and
OL,16,Fselling them at #200 each.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
