OL,5,Ccartridges
OL,7,FWhen confronted, she told bosses that
OL,8,Fshe had been committing the thefts
OL,9,Fsince 2019, but investigations
OL,10,Frevealed her criminality had gone back
OL,11,Fmuch further. Her employment has since
OL,12,Fbeen terminated.
OL,14,FMr Eskdale said: "In 2016, 130
OL,15,Fcartridges had been bought at #10,457.
OL,16,FIn 2017, 251 had been bought, costing
OL,17,F#21,340. In 2018, #12,710. In 2019,
OL,18,F#5,645 - though this coincides with
OL,19,Fthe defendant's maternity leave.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
