OL,7,F"In 2020, 194 cartridges were bought
OL,8,Fat #16,480. In 2021, 295 were bought
OL,9,Fat #23,868. In 2022, 391 were bought
OL,10,Fat #34,749. In 2023, 429 were bought
OL,11,Fat #40, 593. And in 2024, 230 were
OL,12,Fbought at #24,233."
OL,14,FIn total the unauthorised payment
OL,15,Famounted to #188,665, and Timmins
OL,16,Fadmitted the offence to police in her
OL,17,Finterview, following her arrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
