OL,7,FJudge Peter Morgan adjourned the
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing to allow for
OL,9,Fprosecutors to establish whether the
OL,10,Fcompany seeks compensation, and if
OL,11,Fthey wished to provide a victim impact
OL,12,Fstatement. He also asked defence
OL,13,Fcounsel to provide medical evidence
OL,14,Frelating to Timmins' mum.
OL,16,FTimmins, of Cumberland Avenue,
OL,17,FSalford, will be sentenced on January
OL,18,F19 next year. She pleaded guilty at an
OL,19,Fearlier hearing to theft by employee.
